text: "Pincushion" is a 1994 song by ZZ Top and is the leading single from their 11th studio album Antenna. It went to number 15 in the United Kingdom, number 32 in Canada, number 33 in New Zealand, number 40 in Switzerland, number 5 in Finland and number 11 in Sweden. It also went to number 1 on the Billboard Mainstream Rock chart. ==References== Category:1994 songs Category:ZZ Top songs
